{"tid":752991,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"fg3份工唔知點簡好,有冇巴打入黎俾下意見","createTime":"2018-07-23T09:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T15:09:35.000Z","uid":196360,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f835488f78d32188dbd3cb51d8c9c6f5fc1697","tid":752991,"uid":196360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:05:08.000Z","msg":"講翻少少自己既背景先,恒大fg scm first hon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,依家做緊一間中資物流公司既mt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,但最近in 多2份工,搞到自己唔知點簡好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一間<br />\n<br />\n中資物流公司mt(但假假地feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 剛剛入去就叫我expand公司既market,姐係sell野仲要冇commission<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n14k x 15month<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n$50 meal allowance per day<br />\n10AL<br />\n1個半鐘食飯，翻9-5:30<br />\n翻工時間一程40分鐘<br />\n感覺出路麻麻地,因為物流=勿留,而且您係香港人永遠上唔到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二間<br />\n<br />\nFmcg mnc公司,entry 位,做supply chain 既野<br />\n人工around 14k x13<br />\n15AL<br />\n翻9至6，翻工時間15分鐘<br />\n可以日日casual wear<br />\n出路好似好過第一份,只係一開始人工少啲<br />\n<br />\n第三間(最近in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過感覺大機會俾offer)<br />\n<br />\n交通銀行既retail officer trainee=branch trainee<br />\n<br />\n人工應該有16k(睇之前既post知)<br />\nAround 18AL<br />\nOt 唔洗多講<br />\n做跑數狗,大壓力但有爆發力(如果跑到既話)<br />\n<br />\n但做bank姐係直接轉行,因為我讀完supply chain既野唔想做翻依行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外其實我係想做銀行sales多啲,因為冇咁悶同有爆發力,自問外表唔毒,口才都正正常常<br />\n<br />\n我知我係垃圾揾唔到連登仔一半既人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但各位巴打可唔可以俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知未來條路點走好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3a74852967a07d6eb0b5826321a6e154fc681e","tid":752991,"uid":196360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bc8868ede61f2db6e27bebd81169615eb6a89c","tid":752991,"uid":196360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:10:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd5c24a9feafdebb247be24e3bfa58a1e8164b4","tid":752991,"uid":162053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f835488f78d32188dbd3cb51d8c9c6f5fc1697","tid":752991,"uid":196360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:05:08.000Z","msg":"講翻少少自己既背景先,恒大fg scm first hon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk